Interface ImpermanentEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Event
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Concert

    public interface ImpermanentEvent
extends Event
    An impermanent event is an event that has a limited time span, typically restricted to minutes or hours. Although these events are somehow time-lasting, they are considered to be punctual.
